WEBVTT

00:00:01.318 --> 00:00:04.088
At this very moment,

00:00:04.112 --> 00:00:07.011
with every breath we take,

00:00:07.035 --> 00:00:11.958
major delta cities
across the globe are sinking,

00:00:11.982 --> 00:00:14.674
including New York, London,

00:00:14.698 --> 00:00:18.344
Tokyo, Shanghai, New Orleans,

00:00:18.368 --> 00:00:21.389
and as well as my city, Bangkok.

00:00:23.017 --> 00:00:27.009
Here is the usual version
of climate change.

00:00:28.602 --> 00:00:30.030
This is mine.